com.hp.autonomy.aci.content.sort

Class SortBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.autonomy.aci.content.sort.AbstractSort
      • com.hp.autonomy.aci.content.sort.SortBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sort, Iterable<SortBy>

    public class SortBuilder
extends AbstractSort
    A builder for sort expressions. The order of sort specifiers within the builder is significant but the specifiers are deduplicated.
